    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款以卡牌为基础的动作冒险RPG，设定在凯卢姆世界。踏上充满秘密的神秘旅程，收集强大的卡牌，解开这片史诗般土地的谜团，与其他收藏家对战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/b78bc7fe837ba03227beb9ec37088c3b.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/b78bc7fe837ba03227beb9ec37088c3b.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/b78bc7fe837ba03227beb9ec37088c3b.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 非线性世界体验<br>一个向多个方向扩展的世界，您可以自由选择并决定自己作为收藏家和冒险者的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/1bcd6ee7b1338aa30e6f6a1b125f4b56.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/1bcd6ee7b1338aa30e6f6a1b125f4b56.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/1bcd6ee7b1338aa30e6f6a1b125f4b56.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 充满谜团的世界<br>每个角落都可能隐藏着敌人、谜题或秘密。小心前行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.poster.avif?t=1744392942\" width=616 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.webm?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148130/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.mp4?t=1744392942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 卡牌是你的武器<br>在开放世界中使用卡牌的元素来利用局势，或快速组成一手强牌，击败挡路的任何收藏家！</p>",
